  "title": "Front-of-House Ambassador",
  "description": "<p>Payout : $11 - 12/hr</p><p>Date : Long term part time<br />Various Locations : Prime retail locations across Singapore’s Central and Heartland districtsVarious Working Hours : Covering lunch and dinner peak</p><p>Job Summary<br />You will welcome guests to the store, guide them through ordering and payment using an in-house app, manage queues efficiently, encourage guest feedback, and maintain a clean and organized environment during your shift.</p><p></p><p>Responsibilities</p><p>Greet guests warmly and assist them in using the in-house app to place and pay for orders accurately</p><p>Manage customer queues to ensure smooth flow and reduce wait times</p><p>Encourage guests to provide feedback to improve service quality</p><p>Maintain cleanliness and tidiness of the store area throughout the shift</p><p>Perform additional tasks as assigned to support store operations</p><p></p><p>Preferred competencies and qualifications</p><p>-Demonstrate proactive behavior to anticipate and address guest needs</p><p>-Use technology confidently to assist guests with app-based ordering</p><p>-Communicate clearly and effectively to ensure guests understand ordering and payment processes</p><p>-Provide friendly and helpful customer service to enhance guest experience</p><p>-Commit to working three or more days per week, preferably including weekends</p><p></p><p>Require an online interview</p><p>Do drop us a text let us know your name, spoken lang, experience</p><p></p><p>Whatsapp message only : Seth @ 88672972 | Ced @ 83144649 |Niel @ 80932261</p>",
